---
title: Sweet Soy Pan-Seared Tofu with Bok Choy Tossed Rice
description: Sticky sweet and savoury; this tofu will hit all the right notes! Served with garlic-scented bok choy and edamame tossed rice. Dinner couldn't be tastier!
